  "strategy": [
    "Prioritize marker_seen transitions to marker_track for rapid goal approach.",
    "In marker_track, enable move_to_marker; if marker_lost, switch to scan_full to reacquire.",
    "After obstacle detection, always pass through a scan_full state before resuming exploration.",
    "In clear, alternate between move_forward and full_rotate to balance exploration and marker reacquisition.",
    "Use rotate_clockwise in obs_left and rotate_counterclockwise in obs_right to avoid oscillations.",
    "All action/commit states are one-shot: after the action, return to a decision state.",
    "When marker_close is detected in any state, transition to goal_stop and only allow stop.",
    "All uncontrollable events are handled deterministically in every state, ensuring safe and predictable behavior."
